Posts.Title: I found..

Posts.Content:
I'm 23 years old and found a lump in my breast about
 a week ago that hurts like a bruise. I haven't been to the doctors because I was due to start my period and researched that its normal to get lumps when you are about
 to start your menstrual cycle. 
It has yet to disappear but I don't want to bother a doctor for their time over nothing, I just know breast and all kinds of cancer runs in my family so I also want to be smart about
 it. I haven't told anyone about
 it so I guess I'm looking for advice. shall I leave it another week or just go in and get it checked straight away
Thanks in advance,
Jade
